---
title: Ricotta, Bacon and Squash Flatbreads with Crispy Fried Sage
description: We're bringing the flavours of fall in Tuscany to life on a flatbread! Tender squash, earthy sage and creamy ricotta deliver cozy flavours with a hint of sweetness.
